            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stack">
            <h2>Topics Covered</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Static Site Generation (SSG)</li>
              <li>Server-Side Rendering (SSR)</li>
              <li>Client-Side Rendering (CSR)</li>
              <li>Islands Architecture</li>
              <li>Edge Computing</li>
              <li>Content Delivery Networks (CDN)</li>
              <li>And more...</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4" style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
